timeline.bodyText:
Indentation is a bit weird here imo (but not a blocker). I'd suggest:




        Suggested change











                    use: [ {



                      loader: 'lit-css-loader'



                    },  {



                      loader: 'extract-loader'



                    }, {



                      loader: 'css-loader',



                      options: {



                        url: false



                      }



                    }]



                    use: [



                      {



                        loader: 'lit-css-loader'



                      },



                      {



                        loader: 'extract-loader'



                      },



                      {



                        loader: 'css-loader',



                        options: {



                          url: false



                        }



                      }



                    ]






or




        Suggested change











                    use: [ {



                      loader: 'lit-css-loader'



                    },  {



                      loader: 'extract-loader'



                    }, {



                      loader: 'css-loader',



                      options: {



                        url: false



                      }



                    }]



                    use: [



                      { loader: 'lit-css-loader' },



                      { loader: 'extract-loader' },



                      {



                        loader: 'css-loader',



                        options: {



                          url: false



                        }



                      }



                    ]

